Hi,
the following code
```
fun main() {
    var sum = 0L
    sum += mapOf(1 to 1).getOrDefault(100L, 0)
}
```
produces a compiler error for 1.3.72.  The code is buggy (uses a Long as key for a Map with Int keys).
